1. *Boja* mu je plava. (His color is blue.)
2. Ona je prelepih *boja*. (She has beautiful colors.)
3. On voli da se igra sa raznim *bojama*. (He likes to play with different colors.)
4. Ona je bojila zid u svojoj sobi. (She painted the wall in her room.)
5. Oni su se igrali sa bojicama. (They were playing with crayons.)
6. *Boja* njegove majice je crvena. (The color of his shirt is red.)
7. On se boji da nešto ne pogreši. (He is afraid of making a mistake.)
8. Ona je bojila kosu plavom. (She dyed her hair blue.)